<font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>遵命</b></font>

107
00:08:28,660 --> 00:08:30,330
<font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>是...是</b></font>

108
00:08:30,840 --> 00:08:31,730
<font face="枫雪古印体" size="32"><b>明白了</b></font>

109
00:08:31,730 --> 00:08:33,150
